## Configuration

### Environment Variables

Create a `.env` file in project root:

```env
# Application
APP__APP_NAME={{ project_name }}
APP__DEBUG=false
APP__ENVIRONMENT=development

# Logging
LOGGING__LOG_LEVEL=INFO
LOGGING__LOG_FILE=logs/app.log

# Paths
PATHS__DATA_DIR=data
PATHS__LOGS_DIR=logs
```

## Development

### Code Quality Tools

```bash
# Format code with Ruff
ruff format src/ tests/

# Lint with Ruff
ruff check src/ tests/

# Type checking with mypy
mypy src/

# Type checking with ty (faster alternative)
ty src/

# Run all quality checks
ruff format src/ tests/ && ruff check src/ tests/ && mypy src/
```

### Testing

```bash
# Run tests
pytest

# Run specific test file
pytest tests/
```

